<h1>Post</h1>

<p>Blog 3.5 is here! You can download it via the link in My Tools to the right. Blog 3.5 contains many big improvements including multiple blogs per dsn, multiple users per blog, and alias support. Download, read the docs, and enjoy. If you run into a bug, please post it to the <a href="http://www.camdenfamily.com/morpheus/forums/forums.cfm?conferenceid=4">BlogCFC Forum</a>.</p>
<p>As always, BlogCFC is free for all. If you enjoy it I ask that you please donate to my Amazon wish list.</p>
